v2.0.4
Zev-7.bin

Recent updates:
- Hardware version selector: hold SW2 at power-on to cycle the version; shown on the first tube, then reboots into it
- Version stored in its own permanent "Zsys" NVS namespace — survives factory reset
- "Ruby" namespace is now security-only (accepts any valid Zev code + chip signature); variant no longer derived from the code
- Under-lighting now present on all units
- ver 0 = standard (neons swapped), ver 1 = neons not swapped
